This license applies to the SIDfinity pipeline code (src/), documentation
(docs/), and the V2 player code generator (src/player/codegen_v2.py).

The following components have separate licenses:

  tools/siddump.cpp      GPL v2 (links libsidplayfp)
  tools/sidrender.cpp    GPL v2 (links libsidplayfp)
  tools/test_libsid.cpp  GPL v2 (links libsidplayfp)
  tools/gt2asm.c         GPL v2 (wraps GoatTracker assembler code)
  tools/libsidplayfp/    GPL v2 (see tools/libsidplayfp/COPYING)
  tools/xa65/            GPL v2 (see tools/xa65/xa/COPYING)

The SIDfinity player algorithms are based on Lasse Öörni's GoatTracker V2
playroutine, released under the following terms:

  "This playroutine source code does not fall under the GPL license!
   Use it, or song binaries created from it freely for any purpose,
   commercial or noncommercial."
